### Tender Description
A meeting of the Marine Industrial Advisory Committee (MIAC) took place on October 26th and 27th, 2022, in Ottawa. The meeting brought together government officials and industry representatives to discuss various topics, including industrial technical benefits, Indigenous procurement, marine human resources, and more. Presentations from the meeting are included in the attached documents. Further information on the meeting can be found in the MIAC Summary Report October 2022.
